        <title>FolderItem object</title>
        <paragraph><literal>app.project.FolderItem</literal></paragraph>
        <paragraph><strong>Description</strong></paragraph>
        <paragraph>The FolderItem object corresponds to a folder in your Project panel. It can contain various types of items (footage, compositions, solids) as well as other folders.</paragraph>
