                <title>FolderItem.numItems</title>
                <paragraph><literal>app.project.item(index).numItems</literal></paragraph>
                <paragraph><strong>Description</strong></paragraph>
                <paragraph>The number of items contained in the items collection (<literal>folderItem.items.length</literal>).</paragraph>
                <paragraph>If the folder contains another folder, only the FolderItem for that folder is counted, not any subitems contained in it.</paragraph>
                <paragraph><strong>Type</strong></paragraph>
                <paragraph>Integer; read-only.</paragraph>
